abstract: YONKERS, June 13 The International Pacing Series still had one race to go, Thursday night's $50,000 National Championship Pace at 1 miles, but most of the talk around Yonkers Raceway today centered on trotters.

abstract: LOCUST VALLEY, L.I., June 13 Miss Melissa Hattersley, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Robert C. Hattersley, was married this afternoon to William Schnirring, son of Mr. and Mrs. F.W. Schnirring of Larchmont, N.Y., and Fort Lauderdale, Fla.
